				<h2>Is the copy editor badge not working?</h2>
<p>According to <a href="https://apple.stackexchange.com/badges/33/copy-editor">the description of the copy editor badge</a>, the requirement is for you to edit 500 posts. I have done that and I don't see the badge. If you look on <a href="https://apple.stackexchange.com/users?tab=editors&amp;filter=all">the users page</a>, you'll notice that both bmike and I have edited more than 500 posts. Why don't I have a badge?</p>

